description: This is the extract of the fruits of Citrus junos , Cucurbita pepo, Fragaria ananassa, Lens esculenta, Pyrus malus, Pyrus pyrifolia, and Solanum lycopersicum; the kernels of Zea mays; the leaves of Arctium lappa , Brassica oleracea acephala , Brassica oleracea capitata, Camellia sinensis , Moringa oleifera , Raphanus sativus, and Spinacia oleracea; the leaves and stems of Sorghum bicolor ; the meal of Avena sativa; the pulp of Solanum tuberosum; the roots of Daucus carota, Dioscorea oppositifolia, Nelumbo nucifera , and Raphanus sativus; the seeds of Amaranthus hypochondriacus , Anacardium occidentale, Cicer arietinum , Coix lacryma-Jobi ma-yuen , Glycine max, Macadamia ternifolia , Oryza sativa, Phaseolus angularis , Pistacia vera , Prunus amygdalus dulcis, Rhynchosia nulubilis , Sesamum indicum, Setaria italica , and Triticum turgidum; the sprouts of Hordeum vulgare ; the tubers of Cyperus esculentus ; the whole plants, Artemisia princeps , Brassica oleracea italica, Chenopodium quinoa , Enteromorpha compressa , Hordeum vulgare , Ipomoea batatas , Laminaria japonica , Lentinus edodes , Pleurotus ostreatus , Porphyra tenera , and Undaria pinnatifida.
